## Bootstrap confidence sets

:::: {.columns .v-center-container}

::: {.column width="60%"}
::: {.content-box-purple .footnotesize}
**Given:** $D = \DelGreen + \EpsRed$

[**1.** $\hX = \mds(D, p)$]{.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=1}

[**2.** Compute the residuals $\color{purple}{E} = D - \Del(\hX)$]{.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=2}

[**3.** For $b = 1, \ldots, B$:]{.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=3}

[&emsp; **3.1** **Externally randomize** $\color{purple}{E}$ to get $\EpsRed\b$]{.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=3}

::: {.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=4}
&emsp; &emsp; &emsp; **• Empirical (Efron's):** &nbsp; $\color{red}{\eps_{ij}} \sim_{\text{iid}} (e_{ij})$ with replacement+br
&emsp; &emsp; &emsp; **• Mutliplier:** &emsp;&emsp;&emsp; $\color{red}{\eps_{ij}} = e_{ij} \cdot r_{ij}$ where $r_{ij} \sim_{\text{iid}} N(0, 1)$
:::

[&emsp; **3.2** Generate noisy dissimilarities $D\b = \Del(\hX) + \EpsRed\b$]{.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=5}

[&emsp; **3.3** Compute $\hX\b = \mds(D\b, p)$]{.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=6}

[&emsp; **3.4** Compute $\hat T_n\b = \max_{i}\|\hOm^{-1/2}(\hx_i - \hgc\b(\hx_i\b))\|$ via **Procrustes**]{.fragment .fade-in-then-semi-out fragment-index=6}

[**4.** Compute the **bootstrap quantile** &nbsp;$q_{1-\alpha}\b$&nbsp; of &nbsp; $\{\hat T_n\b(1), \dots, \hat T_n\b(B)\}$]{.fragment fragment-index=7}

**Return:** $\displaystyle\conf_{\alpha, i} := \ellipse\big( \hx_i,\; \hOm_i,\;\; q\b_{1-\alpha} \big)$ for $i=1, \dots, n$

